00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:15.083 align:middle
Such beauty.

00:00:16.875 --> 00:00:18.292 align:middle
--[KAMINSKI] Behold!
--[KLARA shrieking]

00:00:18.375 --> 00:00:21.333 align:middle
[KAMINSKI] This is the true
form of God's angel!

00:00:21.417 --> 00:00:24.000 align:middle
[shrieking continues]

00:00:25.542 --> 00:00:26.625 align:middle
[snarls]

00:00:26.708 --> 00:00:29.542 align:middle
Yes! You're ready
to fulfill your destiny!

00:00:29.625 --> 00:00:31.167 align:middle
Come here!

00:00:33.417 --> 00:00:35.125 align:middle
[KLARA growling]

00:00:35.208 --> 00:00:37.333 align:middle
No! Don't!

00:00:37.417 --> 00:00:39.083 align:middle
[KLARA snarls]

00:00:39.167 --> 00:00:40.583 align:middle
[screams]

00:00:42.542 --> 00:00:43.750 align:middle
Sakura!

00:00:45.167 --> 00:00:47.125 align:middle
[SAKURA whimpering]

00:00:59.208 --> 00:01:00.333 align:middle
Stop it, Klara!

00:01:00.417 --> 00:01:02.458 align:middle
If you stay in this form
for much longer,

00:01:02.542 --> 00:01:04.458 align:middle
you won't be able to turn back!

00:01:06.583 --> 00:01:09.000 align:middle
That's enough of you!

00:01:09.083 --> 00:01:10.208 align:middle
[ANASTASIA grunts]

00:01:11.208 --> 00:01:12.333 align:middle
Anastasia!

00:01:12.417 --> 00:01:13.333 align:middle
[ANASTASIA growls]

00:01:13.417 --> 00:01:14.958 align:middle
[yells]

00:01:17.458 --> 00:01:18.500 align:middle
[gasps]

00:01:20.458 --> 00:01:23.083 align:middle
Sakura!

00:01:23.167 --> 00:01:24.208 align:middle
Klara.

00:01:25.708 --> 00:01:27.083 align:middle
She's part of our family.

00:01:28.125 --> 00:01:29.417 align:middle
Save her!

00:01:29.500 --> 00:01:31.500 align:middle
It's up to you!

00:01:31.583 --> 00:01:32.917 align:middle
[FLOWER DIVISION]
Sakura!

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:34.250 align:middle
[SAKURA gasps]

00:01:37.458 --> 00:01:40.625 align:middle
[KLARA growling]

00:01:40.708 --> 00:01:42.542 align:middle
[snarls]

00:01:42.625 --> 00:01:44.500 align:middle
It'll be all right.

00:01:48.208 --> 00:01:49.292 align:middle
[snarls]

00:01:49.375 --> 00:01:50.625 align:middle
[grunts]

00:01:52.458 --> 00:01:54.917 align:middle
It's okay, Klara...

00:01:58.500 --> 00:02:00.875 align:middle
You have to trust me.

00:02:00.958 --> 00:02:02.542 align:middle
[snarls]

00:02:02.625 --> 00:02:04.042 align:middle
[SAKURA yelps]

00:02:04.125 --> 00:02:05.625 align:middle
[whimpers]

00:02:10.458 --> 00:02:11.750 align:middle
[gasps]

00:02:13.667 --> 00:02:15.250 align:middle
[SAKURA]
Klara...

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:39.458 align:middle
[SAKURA gasps]

00:02:49.583 --> 00:02:53.167 align:middle
Remember me, Klara.

00:02:53.250 --> 00:02:57.208 align:middle
Remember the people who
truly love you as much as I do.

00:02:57.292 --> 00:02:59.042 align:middle
Remember those
that protected you

00:02:59.125 --> 00:03:00.875 align:middle
and wished for your happiness.

00:03:00.958 --> 00:03:03.375 align:middle
Remember Leyla.

00:03:03.458 --> 00:03:05.875 align:middle
Come back. Remember us.

00:03:15.208 --> 00:03:18.000 align:middle
I can't... I shouldn't...

00:03:18.083 --> 00:03:22.583 align:middle
The people I meet--
everything I touch suffers.

00:03:22.667 --> 00:03:25.833 align:middle
Klara, you won't hurt us.

00:03:25.917 --> 00:03:29.333 align:middle
I wish I could show you
what I've always seen.

00:03:29.417 --> 00:03:30.958 align:middle
I only see hope.

00:03:31.042 --> 00:03:32.375 align:middle
[gasps]

00:03:34.833 --> 00:03:36.542 align:middle
Nadezhda...

00:03:46.625 --> 00:03:48.375 align:middle
Sakura...

00:03:48.458 --> 00:03:49.750 align:middle
Klara...

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:04.500 align:middle
Welcome home, Klara.

00:04:04.583 --> 00:04:07.542 align:middle
Sakura, thank you.

00:04:07.625 --> 00:04:09.125 align:middle
What are you doing?!

00:04:12.167 --> 00:04:13.083 align:middle
[KAMINSKI growls]

00:04:13.167 --> 00:04:14.917 align:middle
--Yah!
--[KAMINSKI grunts]

00:04:18.667 --> 00:04:21.667 align:middle
This farce is over, Kaminski.

00:04:21.750 --> 00:04:23.042 align:middle
Yield.

00:04:23.125 --> 00:04:25.625 align:middle
[KAMINSKI chuckles]

00:04:25.708 --> 00:04:29.333 align:middle
[cackles]

00:04:29.417 --> 00:04:31.167 align:middle
You haven't figured
out the Sevastopol's

00:04:31.250 --> 00:04:33.542 align:middle
--true purpose, have you?
--[HAKUSHU] What?

00:04:33.625 --> 00:04:35.917 align:middle
It can absorb the energy
of a half-demon,

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:37.750 align:middle
you foolish creatures!

00:04:42.667 --> 00:04:44.167 align:middle
Now bear witness!

00:04:44.250 --> 00:04:46.250 align:middle
God's true face is
about to be revealed

00:04:46.333 --> 00:04:48.542 align:middle
for all His new world to see!

00:04:56.167 --> 00:04:57.750 align:middle
[BOTH whimper]

00:04:59.125 --> 00:05:00.542 align:middle
[BOTH gasp]

00:05:09.833 --> 00:05:10.750 align:middle
[gasps]

00:05:10.833 --> 00:05:13.083 align:middle
What's this? Master?

00:05:13.167 --> 00:05:16.333 align:middle
This is an abomination, Sakura.

00:05:16.417 --> 00:05:18.167 align:middle
[KAMINSKI]
An abomination?

00:05:18.250 --> 00:05:20.292 align:middle
How short-sighted.

00:05:20.375 --> 00:05:24.333 align:middle
My new form is divine
splendor exemplified.

00:05:24.417 --> 00:05:27.917 align:middle
Much obliged, Leyla, Klara.

00:05:29.125 --> 00:05:30.792 align:middle
[KAMINSKI]
After all, it was your power

00:05:30.875 --> 00:05:32.875 align:middle
stored within the Sevastopol.

00:05:32.958 --> 00:05:35.583 align:middle
I'm sanctified. Ascended.

00:05:35.667 --> 00:05:39.583 align:middle
Take comfort knowing you brought
forth your new Almighty.

00:05:39.667 --> 00:05:42.875 align:middle
You've served
your purpose, Klara.

00:05:42.958 --> 00:05:46.000 align:middle
Kneel before me
and await God's judgment.

00:05:47.458 --> 00:05:48.667 align:middle
[gasping]

00:05:51.667 --> 00:05:53.708 align:middle
[HAKUSHU]
Sakura. I'll take Klara.

00:05:53.792 --> 00:05:55.750 align:middle
I suggest you
get to the Obu now.

00:05:55.833 --> 00:05:56.917 align:middle
Right!

00:05:58.750 --> 00:05:59.917 align:middle
[KAMINSKI]
Hmph.

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:06.667 align:middle
--[KAMINSKI] Tch.
--[CLARISSA shrieks]

00:06:06.750 --> 00:06:07.875 align:middle
Heh!

00:06:11.917 --> 00:06:14.375 align:middle
[SAKURA yells]

00:06:15.917 --> 00:06:17.042 align:middle
Heh.

00:06:20.333 --> 00:06:21.250 align:middle
[gasps]

00:06:21.333 --> 00:06:22.792 align:middle
[KAMINSKI]
Hyah!

00:06:22.875 --> 00:06:24.958 align:middle
[SAKURA grunts]

00:06:25.042 --> 00:06:27.458 align:middle
[laughs]

00:06:27.542 --> 00:06:29.083 align:middle
It all ends here.

00:06:29.167 --> 00:06:30.958 align:middle
Dasvidaniya.

00:06:31.042 --> 00:06:33.125 align:middle
It's been interesting, dear.

00:06:36.542 --> 00:06:37.750 align:middle
[ANASTASIA]
Tch.

00:06:45.875 --> 00:06:48.458 align:middle
I'm here, girls. Let's go!

00:06:48.542 --> 00:06:51.042 align:middle
Sakura! Sorry we're late!

00:06:51.125 --> 00:06:52.917 align:middle
Attention Flower Division!

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:54.625 align:middle
Evasive maneuvers now!

00:06:54.708 --> 00:06:56.833 align:middle
Keep your distance
from the Sevastopol!

00:06:56.917 --> 00:06:59.833 align:middle
Focus all fire power
on main defenses!

00:07:03.417 --> 00:07:04.875 align:middle
Seijuro...

00:07:06.667 --> 00:07:08.875 align:middle
[KLARA]
Everyone! This way!

00:07:08.958 --> 00:07:10.917 align:middle
[SAKURA]
Flower Division, fall back!

00:07:12.208 --> 00:07:13.500 align:middle
No, you don't!

00:07:15.250 --> 00:07:16.375 align:middle
Master!

00:07:16.458 --> 00:07:19.333 align:middle
Leave everything to me.
Get out of here!

00:07:20.542 --> 00:07:22.375 align:middle
--[SAKURA] Master!
--[HATSUHO] Sakura!

00:07:22.458 --> 00:07:24.083 align:middle
You've seen what she can do.

00:07:24.167 --> 00:07:25.583 align:middle
She'll be fine.

00:07:27.875 --> 00:07:29.000 align:middle
[SAKURA]
Mm.

00:07:32.875 --> 00:07:34.458 align:middle
[KAMIYAMA]
Sakura! I'm on the move.

00:07:34.542 --> 00:07:36.625 align:middle
I'll bring transport
starboard side.

00:07:36.708 --> 00:07:38.917 align:middle
Await further instruction
from Commander Kanzaki.

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:40.583 align:middle
--Understand?
--[SAKURA] Roger!

00:07:40.667 --> 00:07:42.625 align:middle
Everyone, jump!

00:07:45.583 --> 00:07:46.833 align:middle
[KLARA grunts]

00:07:48.750 --> 00:07:50.833 align:middle
Hard to starboard now!

00:07:53.125 --> 00:07:54.667 align:middle
Fire!

00:08:01.333 --> 00:08:02.583 align:middle
Master...

00:08:02.667 --> 00:08:04.000 align:middle
[gasps]

00:08:06.042 --> 00:08:07.333 align:middle
[SAKURA]
Hakushu!

00:08:12.542 --> 00:08:14.083 align:middle
[KOMACHI]
The Sevastopol's fallen.

00:08:14.167 --> 00:08:15.750 align:middle
It's finished for now.

00:08:20.250 --> 00:08:22.167 align:middle
[SAKURA]
Master, where's Kaminski?

00:08:22.250 --> 00:08:24.000 align:middle
I lost track of him.

00:08:24.083 --> 00:08:26.083 align:middle
No matter.

00:08:26.167 --> 00:08:28.542 align:middle
I doubt he could survive
something like this,

00:08:28.625 --> 00:08:30.458 align:middle
even with his abilities.

00:08:36.208 --> 00:08:37.500 align:middle
[KLARA grunts]

00:08:48.375 --> 00:08:49.292 align:middle
[alarm blares]

00:08:49.375 --> 00:08:51.333 align:middle
[KAMIYAMA gasps]
Status report!

00:08:51.417 --> 00:08:52.792 align:middle
[CREWMAN 12A] Unidentified
heat signature coming

00:08:52.875 --> 00:08:54.000 align:middle
from below, sir.

00:08:54.083 --> 00:08:55.583 align:middle
Not good.

00:08:58.500 --> 00:09:01.208 align:middle
[KAMIYAMA grunts]
What happened?!

00:09:01.292 --> 00:09:03.667 align:middle
[CREWMAN 12A]
Attack from underwater!

00:09:03.750 --> 00:09:04.792 align:middle
No...

00:09:04.875 --> 00:09:06.375 align:middle
It can't be...

00:09:15.042 --> 00:09:16.333 align:middle
Impossible.

00:09:26.542 --> 00:09:28.708 align:middle
[KLARA shrieks]

00:09:28.792 --> 00:09:31.708 align:middle
[KAMINSKI laughs maniacally]

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:35.250 align:middle
I told you.

00:09:35.333 --> 00:09:37.583 align:middle
I am your God now!

00:09:37.667 --> 00:09:42.208 align:middle
Cower before me,
you impudent mortals.

00:09:42.292 --> 00:09:45.958 align:middle
Take heed for the bells
of the apocalypse have rung!

00:09:56.042 --> 00:09:59.250 align:middle
[cackles]

00:10:02.333 --> 00:10:04.792 align:middle
[alarm blaring]

00:10:04.875 --> 00:10:07.000 align:middle
[KAMIYAMA] We'll crash land
the skip on the water.

00:10:07.083 --> 00:10:09.500 align:middle
Everyone, brace for impact.

00:10:09.583 --> 00:10:12.375 align:middle
I'm going to my Mugen.
You take command!

00:10:12.458 --> 00:10:13.417 align:middle
[CREWMAN 12A]
Yes, sir!

00:10:13.500 --> 00:10:15.083 align:middle
Seijuro!

00:10:15.167 --> 00:10:17.708 align:middle
Klara? Find a safe
place to ride this out.

00:10:17.792 --> 00:10:20.500 align:middle
[KLARA]
No. This is my fight!

00:10:20.583 --> 00:10:21.833 align:middle
[KAMIYAMA gasps]

00:10:24.500 --> 00:10:28.708 align:middle
Captain, you once told me I was
part of the Flower Division.

00:10:28.792 --> 00:10:30.958 align:middle
I won't hide while others fight!

00:10:33.333 --> 00:10:34.792 align:middle
You sure about this?

00:10:34.875 --> 00:10:37.083 align:middle
Yes.

00:10:37.167 --> 00:10:38.625 align:middle
Okay.

00:10:38.708 --> 00:10:41.792 align:middle
Imperial Combat Revue, roll out!

00:10:55.458 --> 00:10:57.583 align:middle
Eisen-Jäger, let's Go!

00:10:57.667 --> 00:11:00.125 align:middle
Wanglong, Yui Huang, I'm Ready!

00:11:00.208 --> 00:11:03.000 align:middle
Lancelot, launching
in the Bridwen now!

00:11:10.750 --> 00:11:12.375 align:middle
[LANCELOT yells]

00:11:17.958 --> 00:11:19.250 align:middle
[YUI]
Haah!

00:11:34.583 --> 00:11:36.958 align:middle
[HATSUHO bellows]

00:11:38.167 --> 00:11:39.625 align:middle
Here we go!

00:11:44.167 --> 00:11:45.250 align:middle
[BOTH scream]

00:11:45.333 --> 00:11:48.333 align:middle
[screaming]

00:11:48.417 --> 00:11:51.125 align:middle
[KAMINSKI cackles]

00:11:51.208 --> 00:11:54.042 align:middle
You're foolish to
disobey God's will.

00:11:54.125 --> 00:11:58.333 align:middle
Your spirit power and metal
is no match for the Almighty.

00:11:58.417 --> 00:12:00.958 align:middle
Wallow and wither
in your feebleness.

00:12:01.042 --> 00:12:05.250 align:middle
All you can do in the end is
witness the foreordained.

00:12:05.333 --> 00:12:07.083 align:middle
[SAKURA] Kaminski's going
for the capital!

00:12:07.167 --> 00:12:08.417 align:middle
[LANCELOT]
Stop him!

00:12:10.125 --> 00:12:11.667 align:middle
[KAMINSKI]
Such a shame.

00:12:11.750 --> 00:12:13.750 align:middle
But if it's a fight you want.

00:12:17.042 --> 00:12:18.250 align:middle
[gasps]

00:12:24.333 --> 00:12:26.667 align:middle
[HATSUHO grunts]
There're so many!

00:12:26.750 --> 00:12:28.833 align:middle
[ANASTASIA]
Tokyo will be overrun!

00:12:40.833 --> 00:12:43.375 align:middle
Kaminski's golem has
reached the district, ma'am.

00:12:43.458 --> 00:12:45.083 align:middle
There's a large
energy signature!

00:12:45.167 --> 00:12:46.250 align:middle
[alarm blaring]

00:12:46.333 --> 00:12:47.500 align:middle
[gasps]

00:12:47.583 --> 00:12:49.167 align:middle
[blaring continues]

00:12:49.250 --> 00:12:50.875 align:middle
[SAKURA whimpers]

00:12:50.958 --> 00:12:52.125 align:middle
[gasps]

00:12:55.500 --> 00:12:56.833 align:middle
[SAKURA gasps]

00:12:58.292 --> 00:12:59.750 align:middle
Who's that...?

00:13:12.667 --> 00:13:14.708 align:middle
It was built for this.

00:13:14.792 --> 00:13:16.417 align:middle
Tenjin!

00:13:16.500 --> 00:13:17.458 align:middle
[KLARA]
Sakura!

00:13:17.542 --> 00:13:18.917 align:middle
[SAKURA]
Klara...?

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:21.000 align:middle
What are you doing here?

00:13:21.083 --> 00:13:22.000 align:middle
She wants to help!

00:13:22.083 --> 00:13:23.792 align:middle
Uh? Captain?

00:13:23.875 --> 00:13:25.708 align:middle
[KAMIYAMA]
Let's end this, Kaminski!

00:13:26.667 --> 00:13:29.708 align:middle
[KAMINSKI] It doesn't matter
how many of you there are.

00:13:31.458 --> 00:13:32.833 align:middle
The hell?

00:13:34.500 --> 00:13:36.125 align:middle
[gasps]

00:13:50.167 --> 00:13:51.583 align:middle
All right!

00:13:51.667 --> 00:13:55.083 align:middle
Why don't we return to our
regularly scheduled program?!

00:13:56.917 --> 00:13:59.875 align:middle
[HAKUSHU] The weak point
is there at his chest!

00:13:59.958 --> 00:14:01.958 align:middle
Now go get to work!

00:14:02.042 --> 00:14:03.458 align:middle
[ALL]
Right!

00:14:07.583 --> 00:14:09.708 align:middle
[HATSUHO yells]

00:14:10.458 --> 00:14:12.375 align:middle
--[gasps]
--Told you, didn't I?

00:14:12.458 --> 00:14:14.792 align:middle
Nothing you can do will harm me!

00:14:14.875 --> 00:14:16.375 align:middle
[HATSUHO grunts]

00:14:16.458 --> 00:14:17.875 align:middle
[CLARISSA grunting]

00:14:27.500 --> 00:14:29.833 align:middle
Tch! It's a barrier!

00:14:32.292 --> 00:14:33.333 align:middle
Ah, hell.

00:14:33.417 --> 00:14:34.958 align:middle
He's charging up for a blast!

00:14:35.042 --> 00:14:38.500 align:middle
[CLARISSA]
Auster Plagas Concursus!

00:14:38.583 --> 00:14:43.542 align:middle
This is farewell, Tokyo...!

00:14:51.375 --> 00:14:53.958 align:middle
[CLARISSA whimpering]

00:14:54.042 --> 00:14:57.042 align:middle
[laughs]
You're all hopeless!

00:14:57.125 --> 00:14:59.083 align:middle
[CLARISSA grunting]

00:15:01.542 --> 00:15:02.500 align:middle
[gasps]

00:15:04.125 --> 00:15:05.667 align:middle
I've got you.

00:15:10.542 --> 00:15:11.833 align:middle
[CLARISSA]
Everyone!

00:15:11.917 --> 00:15:13.125 align:middle
Don't give up!

00:15:13.208 --> 00:15:14.583 align:middle
You can do this!

00:15:14.667 --> 00:15:16.208 align:middle
[KAMINSKI]
It's useless!

00:15:20.333 --> 00:15:22.333 align:middle
Your times up, just give in!

00:15:29.375 --> 00:15:33.917 align:middle
[HAKUSHU bellows]

00:15:34.000 --> 00:15:35.042 align:middle
This power...

00:15:35.125 --> 00:15:36.958 align:middle
We've felt it before!

00:15:37.042 --> 00:15:38.667 align:middle
Keep going!

00:15:38.750 --> 00:15:40.208 align:middle
Right!

00:15:49.333 --> 00:15:50.875 align:middle
[SAKURA]
Oh, no!

00:15:53.208 --> 00:15:54.792 align:middle
Everyone is fine!

00:15:54.875 --> 00:15:56.167 align:middle
Finish this, Sakura!

00:15:56.250 --> 00:15:57.708 align:middle
[HATSUHO]
Come on, you two.

00:15:57.792 --> 00:15:59.417 align:middle
We're counting on you!

00:15:59.500 --> 00:16:01.500 align:middle
[KAMINSKI snarls]

00:16:01.583 --> 00:16:04.625 align:middle
[yells]

00:16:04.708 --> 00:16:06.542 align:middle
You'll pay for that dearly.

00:16:06.625 --> 00:16:08.875 align:middle
With your lives!

00:16:10.500 --> 00:16:11.458 align:middle
[SAKURA]
Klara?

00:16:11.542 --> 00:16:13.250 align:middle
He has to be stopped!

00:16:13.333 --> 00:16:15.625 align:middle
[KLARA]
Yes!

00:16:15.708 --> 00:16:16.875 align:middle
[KANZAKI]
Look, Father.

00:16:16.958 --> 00:16:21.375 align:middle
Sakura. This is the power
I failed to wield.

00:16:24.000 --> 00:16:25.583 align:middle
[KANZAKI]
But that was before.

00:16:25.667 --> 00:16:27.208 align:middle
I'm using it now!

00:16:27.292 --> 00:16:28.542 align:middle
You must merge!

00:16:28.625 --> 00:16:29.667 align:middle
Amamiya!

00:16:29.750 --> 00:16:30.708 align:middle
Klara!

00:16:30.792 --> 00:16:31.958 align:middle
[BOTH gasp]

00:16:32.042 --> 00:16:34.458 align:middle
The Tenjin was developed
for a special purpose.

00:16:34.542 --> 00:16:36.417 align:middle
Together it allows
the Prototype Obu

00:16:36.500 --> 00:16:38.750 align:middle
to fully utilize its abilities!

00:16:38.833 --> 00:16:41.083 align:middle
Once you've combined,
you'll be powerful enough

00:16:41.167 --> 00:16:42.708 align:middle
to stop Kaminski!

